description:
Knowsley Council require a contractor to remodel and refurbish the Kirkby Centre to accommodate the Alt Bridge post-16 provision.
The outline scope of the works is as follows:
•	Site set up;
•	Site preparation & strip out;
•	Structural alterations
•	Install passenger lift
•	External works including new road layout
•	Installing fencing
•	M&E amendments;
•	Fitting out;
